{"tid":1938581,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【武漢肺炎】國際文憑（IB）課程下月底考試取消 全球逾20萬考生受影響","createTime":"2020-03-22T15:41:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-22T16:11:15.000Z","uid":129513,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8355bb089f8823db63cb6d4b5e033b7e7937a6a5","tid":1938581,"uid":129513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T15:41:58.000Z","msg":"國際文憑組織（International Baccalaureate，IB）向學校及家長發信，指受武漢肺炎疫情在全球多國蔓延影響，將取消原定於4月底至5月中舉行的IB課程考試，估計全球有逾20萬名考生受影響。有升學顧問估計，取消IB勢令外國大學在錄取學生時，會索取更多學術及能力證明。<br />\n<br />\n國際文憑組織今日（22日）向學校及家長發信，指組織參考學校、學生、大學及資格認證組織的意見後，決定將4月30日至5月22日舉行的IB課程考試取消。組織形容有關決定是「最負責任及最道德的做法」（most responsible and ethical way forward），並對受影響的考生致歉。<br />\n<br />\n教育界立法會議員葉建源表示，香港每年均有約2、3千人報考IB課程。他指，疫情令多個國家宣佈取消公開試，如英國早前已取消GCSE及A-Level，香港的中學文憑試亦要延期4星期，他會留意事態發展，目前難以估計對有關考生的影響。<br />\n<br />\n而英識教育顧問陳思銘則表示，IB課程除了會計算公開試成績外，也會計算在課程期間的不同評核。他估計外國大學在錄取學生時，或會根據其在校內的預計成績作評估，屆時校方或學生或須向有關大學提供更多學術及能力證明。<br />\n<br />\n現時本港共有33間學校有開辦IB課程，報讀者多為國際學校或英基學校的學生，而香港往年均盛產IB狀元。參考資料，去年本港共有34人在IB試中考獲滿分45分。英基學校協會覆稱，相信國際文憑課程組織將在稍後就今年考試安排發表聲明，若協會有進一步詳情，將會與十三年級生的家長聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200322/2U6N64XJBBG3XXFYHFSH2SQ3PM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200322%2F2U6N64XJBBG3XXFYHFSH2SQ3PM%2F&d=BTQ0Nb6fQhXLRDVXZ5xLdHwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=fd2a7e73\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200322%2F2U6N64XJBBG3XXFYHFSH2SQ3PM%2F&h=3b07fd79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200322/2U6N64XJBBG3XXFYHFSH2SQ3PM/</a>"},{"pid":"7370c47a8c78fca1d876d4a946d6cbe11362aff1","tid":1938581,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T15:43:03.000Z","msg":"IB<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef7222039b5c88464173f6b5881ebd8526226ed5","tid":1938581,"uid":129513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T15:45:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">組織形容有關決定是「最負責任及最道德的做法」（most responsible and ethical way forward），並對受影響的考生致歉。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n考評局：遲啲考囉，有病記得唔好去考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca52e678444c7f5bec6d486cc933d5e07ef2ffe7","tid":1938581,"uid":177955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T16:10:17.000Z","msg":"iB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />AP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nDSE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31cea6729a83ea0723c0ab855659f915034970eb","tid":1938581,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T16:11:15.000Z","msg":"攬炒全世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}